:v-model.description: The number of stars is selected for two-way binding
:v-model.description_zh: 双向绑定选择星星的数量

count.description: The maximum number of stars that can be selected

current.description: The number of stars selected by default is recommended from 1.4.5 onwards in the V-model mode
current.description_zh: 默认选中的星星数量，1.4.5起建议使用v-model方式

size.description: The size of the star, in rpx

inactive-color.description: The color of the star is not selected

active-color.description: The color of the selected star

min-count.description: The minimum number of stars selected

active-icon.description: When selected, the icon name can only be the built-in icon of uView
active-icon.description_zh: 选中时的图标名，只能为uView的内置图标

inactive-icon.description: If the icon name is unchecked, it can only be the built-in icon of uView
inactive-icon.description_zh: 未选中时的图标名，只能为uView的内置图标

custom-prefix.description: This value is required when customizing the font icon library, see: Extending the Custom Icon Library
custom-prefix.description_zh: 自定义字体图标库时，需要写上此值，详见：扩展自定义图标库  (opens new window)

colors.description: The color grading display allows you to distinguish the rating levels with different colors
colors.description_zh: 颜色分级显示，可以用不同颜色区分评分层级

icons.description: Icons are displayed in different categories, and different types of icons can be used to distinguish the rating levels
icons.description_zh: 图标分级显示，可以用不同类型的icon区分评分层级
